Hellplague/ Malice:

The two bots loaded with energon eventually made it back to the holding chamber.  Splattercannon landed outside the room and Hellplague walked into the room.  She handed a cube of energon to Blacknightmare and set two on the bed.  She sat on the bed and tried to awake Malice.

Malice slowly stirred, his systems slowy coming back online.  His optics slowly lit, returning to the red they were usually.  His sight wasn&#39;t one hundred percent though, things were still blurry.  He set up, took a deep breath, let it out, then turned to Hellplague.
&quot;I know you... don&#39;t I?&quot; he asked.
Hellplague scooted close to Malice and put her arms around his shoulders.  She embraced him, then let go to get an energon cube.  SHe handed him th cube before speaking:
&quot;Feed and be well, our pet.  Welcome home, Hunter Killer, the newest of the Minions.&quot;
For a moment, Malice simply stared at her, then grinned, the chuckled, then drank of the energon cube. 

